gomodel:SYNGO_318  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: In this paper, the authors used the fluorescence imaging of FM1-43 dye to investigate the neurotransmitter release in wild type and Synapsin I KO mice. They showed that the number of vesicles that release their content and the total recycling vesicle pool is reduced by 60-70%.. Experimental description: FM 1-43 uptake and release in hippocampal neurons cultured from synapsin I knock-out and wild-type mice." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0808-7003" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3898-5197" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1542-3498" ;
